IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Rebecca Jo LYNCH and Edward James Lynch Upon the Petition of Rebecca Jo Lynch, Petitioner-Appellee/Cross-Appellant, And Concerning Edward James Lynch, Respondent-Appellant/Cross-Appellee. No. 17-2067 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 23, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Edward Lynch appeals, and Rebecca Lynch cross-appeals, a decree of dissolution of marriage. AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED ON APPEAL; AFFIRMED IN PART AND AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED IN PART ON CROSS-APPEAL.

AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED ON APPEAL. AFFIRMED IN PART. AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED IN PART ON CROSS-APPEAL.
